WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )


00:01:05.828 --> 00:01:08.260
=No Doubt In Us=
(Adapted from the Manman comic No Doubt in Us)

00:01:08.388 --> 00:01:11.300
=Episode 22=

00:01:23.879 --> 00:01:26.000
Physician Jiang, how is the Empress?

00:01:26.519 --> 00:01:29.239
Your Majesty, please issue an order
to seal Fengyi Palace now.

00:01:30.719 --> 00:01:31.719
The Empress

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:34.040
has contracted smallpox.

00:01:41.920 --> 00:01:43.200
Please take care of yourself

00:01:43.519 --> 00:01:45.120
and give priority to the empire.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.280
Is there any way to treat her?

00:01:52.519 --> 00:01:53.799
Smallpox is dangerous.

00:01:53.799 --> 00:01:55.040
There is no specific cure.

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:58.680
But I will do my utmost
to care for the Empress.

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:03.040
But this disease
doesn't appear without cause.

00:02:04.079 --> 00:02:05.280
There must be an origin.

00:02:05.760 --> 00:02:06.640
Someone!

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:08.360
Here.

00:02:08.560 --> 00:02:10.159
Investigate thoroughly everything

00:02:10.400 --> 00:02:12.360
the Empress has touched
these past few days.

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:13.039
Yes.

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:21.159
Your Majesty.

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:39.520
Jinyun.

00:02:40.080 --> 00:02:40.800
(Fengyi Palace)
I've investigated.

00:02:41.199 --> 00:02:43.240
Xiao Jinle's belly band
was also sent back then.

00:02:43.719 --> 00:02:45.080
Xu Yu put that one away

00:02:45.080 --> 00:02:46.080
and only kept my own.

00:02:46.759 --> 00:02:48.479
But this rabbit belly band isn't mine.

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:51.159
All those who touched
the belly bands are held.

00:02:51.159 --> 00:02:52.319
We only await interrogation.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:56.479
Since our uncle has already acted,

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:58.840
we need not hesitate any longer.

00:03:06.840 --> 00:03:09.000
I'm here to attend to
Her Majesty. Let me in.

00:03:09.319 --> 00:03:11.800
Your Majesty, are you feeling better?

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:17.039
(Is she genuinely here
to show concern for me?)

00:03:19.560 --> 00:03:20.879
Let Consort Zhao in.

00:03:22.759 --> 00:03:25.919
Your Majesty, you scared me.

00:03:25.919 --> 00:03:26.719
Don't come in!

00:03:27.840 --> 00:03:29.319
I am indeed ill.

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:31.840
I will soon go to the resort palace.

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:36.240
They say you have smallpox.

00:03:37.199 --> 00:03:38.439
You are truly sick?

00:03:39.439 --> 00:03:40.960
Actually, I guessed

00:03:41.800 --> 00:03:43.080
you knew about that matter.

00:03:43.560 --> 00:03:44.240
I'm sorry.

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:45.560
I lied to you.

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:49.879
Luckily, today, I have the chance
to explain it clearly to you.

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:52.479
Now, my heart is unburdened.

00:03:53.319 --> 00:03:57.599
But from now on, managing
the harem will likely fall to you.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:00.500
No.

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:01.340
Don't!

00:04:05.199 --> 00:04:08.680
The one I admire and cherish
now is you, Xu Yu.

00:04:18.439 --> 00:04:19.279
Your Majesty,

00:04:20.160 --> 00:04:23.079
I'll manage the harem well
until your return.

00:04:27.199 --> 00:04:28.399
Thank you, Consort Zhao.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.839
Please return.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:37.319
It's not safe here.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:38.680
Yes.

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:51.319
Xuan.

00:04:53.079 --> 00:04:54.240
Go tell the Emperor.

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:55.839
While I'm still lucid,

00:04:56.920 --> 00:04:58.120
move me to the resort palace.

00:04:58.439 --> 00:04:59.040
Yes.

00:04:59.639 --> 00:05:00.319
I do not agree!

00:05:04.040 --> 00:05:05.360
Your Majesty, you cannot enter!

00:05:07.879 --> 00:05:08.959
The resort palace is far

00:05:09.839 --> 00:05:10.839
and lacks proper care.

00:05:11.319 --> 00:05:12.240
I'll worry about you.

00:05:14.319 --> 00:05:16.319
But the resort palace is spacious.

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:18.680
I can practice my swordplay freely.

00:05:19.079 --> 00:05:20.319
Much more liberating than here.

00:05:20.720 --> 00:05:21.800
How can you still smile?

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:23.800
If I don't smile now,

00:05:23.920 --> 00:05:26.759
when pockmarks are all over my face,
it won't look good when I smile.

00:05:33.680 --> 00:05:34.480
Xu Yu.

00:05:35.439 --> 00:05:36.600
Your Majesty, you can't!

00:05:36.879 --> 00:05:37.759
It risks harm to you.

00:05:41.839 --> 00:05:43.079
Have you ever regretted it?

00:05:43.959 --> 00:05:47.439
Because of my neglect,
you struggled in the palace.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.319
Mother drugged you,

00:05:49.319 --> 00:05:50.519
nearly making you barren,

00:05:50.519 --> 00:05:52.000
and I was completely unaware.

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:56.360
As your husband

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:58.399
and the Emperor,

00:05:59.319 --> 00:06:00.720
I have caused you

00:06:01.959 --> 00:06:03.360
to suffer so much.

00:06:05.920 --> 00:06:06.879
It's all in the past.

00:06:08.079 --> 00:06:09.560
My only concern now

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:11.240
is for you

00:06:11.920 --> 00:06:14.639
and the child I am carrying to be safe.

00:06:15.639 --> 00:06:17.040
I will protect the child.

00:06:17.560 --> 00:06:18.160
No.

00:06:19.680 --> 00:06:21.279
I wish for your safety even more.

00:06:23.439 --> 00:06:24.439
I am right here,

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:26.920
guarding you both.

00:06:27.439 --> 00:06:29.800
What about the people?

00:06:30.360 --> 00:06:33.160
How can Your Majesty jeopardize
the greater good for my sake?

00:06:33.519 --> 00:06:35.079
If you keep disturbing my recovery,

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:37.600
I'll ignore you forever.

00:07:53.439 --> 00:07:54.319
Don't come so close.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:56.399
Examine it from a distance.

00:07:57.800 --> 00:07:58.839
Don't worry.

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:01.759
Since the attendants
who touched it are fine,

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:05.000
it shows this belly band
carries no disease.

00:08:05.439 --> 00:08:06.839
But there must be something else.

00:08:07.339 --> 00:08:09.560
One thing definitely exists on this.

00:08:10.439 --> 00:08:11.360
What is it?

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:16.120
Xiao Jinle's childhood saliva.

00:08:19.800 --> 00:08:20.600
You...

00:08:21.439 --> 00:08:25.120
The only sick person now is the groom
who feeds the Empress's horses.

00:08:25.279 --> 00:08:26.680
All the maids and eunuchs are fine.

00:08:27.360 --> 00:08:29.360
It means there's no disease
on this belly band.

00:08:29.759 --> 00:08:30.399
Perhaps

00:08:32.080 --> 00:08:35.240
it's some kind of cursed object
or sorcery designed to induce illness.

00:08:58.240 --> 00:08:59.720
Why is there a pattern on it?

00:09:04.919 --> 00:09:06.600
This is the talismanic spell.

00:09:07.559 --> 00:09:09.559
Completing the sorcery
requires two conditions.

00:09:10.039 --> 00:09:10.960
First, infect her.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:12.240
Then, cast the spell.

00:09:12.919 --> 00:09:18.159
It seems Prince Ning
used Dada sorcery to unleash smallpox

00:09:18.559 --> 00:09:20.120
to spread plague throughout the city

00:09:20.120 --> 00:09:21.240
and demoralize the people.

00:09:32.039 --> 00:09:32.600
Your Majesty.

00:09:34.159 --> 00:09:34.919
Your medicine.

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:37.240
Jiang Tang.

00:09:37.879 --> 00:09:39.168
Is this smallpox

00:09:40.544 --> 00:09:42.519
Heaven's punishment for me?

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:47.879
Medical texts say it's incurable.

00:09:48.679 --> 00:09:50.320
But there are preventative methods.

00:09:51.039 --> 00:09:52.360
Since it can be prevented,

00:09:53.279 --> 00:09:54.519
it's not Heaven's punishment.

00:09:58.279 --> 00:09:59.840
But all the officials

00:09:59.840 --> 00:10:01.039
and the people in the city

00:10:01.159 --> 00:10:02.639
say so.

00:10:03.559 --> 00:10:06.720
How can His Majesty argue
against them on his own?

00:10:07.639 --> 00:10:09.919
Your Majesty, please take your medicine.

00:10:17.039 --> 00:10:19.279
Your Majesty, how are you?

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:21.679
Your Majesty!

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:25.360
Send word to the palace immediately!

00:10:26.320 --> 00:10:30.080
Tell them Her Majesty
doesn't have much time left.

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:31.039
What?

00:10:31.320 --> 00:10:32.639
Go!

00:10:32.639 --> 00:10:33.200
Yes.

00:10:35.279 --> 00:10:36.720
I know I can't persuade you,

00:10:37.159 --> 00:10:39.039
but the safety of the entire capital

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:42.240
and the entire Chen rests
on your shoulders alone now.

00:10:42.679 --> 00:10:44.320
You must take care of your health.

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:48.320
Sorry

00:10:49.159 --> 00:10:50.360
for making you worry.

00:10:51.559 --> 00:10:54.159
Hearing you haven't eaten lately,

00:10:54.480 --> 00:10:57.039
I specially brought
your favorite pastries.

00:11:01.039 --> 00:11:03.159
Consort Zhao seeks an audience.

00:11:08.759 --> 00:11:09.440
Your Majesty.

00:11:10.559 --> 00:11:14.440
This is the food
we prepared for the Empress.

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:17.600
Please take it to Her Majesty

00:11:18.200 --> 00:11:19.080
and tell her

00:11:19.759 --> 00:11:23.399
we are worried about her.

00:11:24.759 --> 00:11:26.960
Her Majesty must take care of her health

00:11:27.519 --> 00:11:28.720
and return safely.

00:11:29.360 --> 00:11:32.399
This is a sachet I made for the Empress.

00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:36.480
I hope it helps her
sleep peacefully every night.

00:11:37.559 --> 00:11:39.440
We all miss the Empress very much.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:51.559
I...

00:11:53.159 --> 00:11:54.559
Thank you on her behalf.

00:12:25.159 --> 00:12:25.840
Your Majesty.

00:12:26.519 --> 00:12:27.360
You're finally awake.

00:12:30.759 --> 00:12:34.399
Has my condition worsened?

00:12:37.080 --> 00:12:40.039
Does that mean I don't have to
take this bitter medicine anymore?

00:12:50.320 --> 00:12:51.759
You should still take the medicine.

00:12:52.720 --> 00:12:53.679
Regain your strength,

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:57.120
so you can speak with His Majesty.

00:12:57.840 --> 00:12:58.480
His Majesty?

00:12:59.080 --> 00:13:00.639
I've already sent word to His Majesty.

00:13:01.720 --> 00:13:04.480
He should be arriving soon.

00:13:24.240 --> 00:13:24.879
Your Majesty.

00:13:25.600 --> 00:13:27.240
Wear the veil when you see His Majesty

00:13:27.919 --> 00:13:29.840
to leave a somewhat good impression.

00:13:32.879 --> 00:13:33.759
Well...

00:13:35.000 --> 00:13:36.879
I never left a good impression anyway.

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:41.039
Fine, let me put it on.

00:13:54.720 --> 00:13:55.399
Xu Yu!

00:13:55.399 --> 00:13:56.440
Just stay there!

00:13:59.039 --> 00:14:00.000
Don't come any closer.

00:14:05.080 --> 00:14:06.799
They told me to wear the veil,

00:14:07.200 --> 00:14:09.440
afraid I'd leave you
with an ugly impression.

00:14:10.000 --> 00:14:11.480
But looking back,

00:14:12.600 --> 00:14:14.879
I don't think I've left you
with a good impression.

00:14:16.200 --> 00:14:17.960
You never thought I was pretty anyway.

00:14:19.480 --> 00:14:20.320
So,

00:14:28.360 --> 00:14:30.879
whether I have pox marks
or not doesn't really matter.

00:14:32.159 --> 00:14:32.919
Xu Yu.

00:14:32.919 --> 00:14:33.559
Your Majesty.

00:14:34.840 --> 00:14:37.519
I have so much I want to say to you.

00:14:38.840 --> 00:14:40.480
Although I was born a woman,

00:14:41.159 --> 00:14:42.279
in this life,

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:43.639
I've fought on battlefields

00:14:43.799 --> 00:14:45.039
and killed enemies,

00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:47.080
fulfilling my childhood wish.

00:14:48.080 --> 00:14:49.519
I didn't bring shame to my family.

00:14:50.559 --> 00:14:51.879
I don't regret that.

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:55.720
I've liked Your Majesty
since I was little.

00:14:56.639 --> 00:14:57.720
I got to marry you

00:14:58.600 --> 00:15:00.320
but then suffered your misunderstanding.

00:15:01.559 --> 00:15:03.240
Now, we have no doubts about each other.

00:15:04.000 --> 00:15:05.120
I don't regret that.

00:15:06.639 --> 00:15:07.759
I regret.

00:15:09.080 --> 00:15:10.600
I realized it too late.

00:15:11.440 --> 00:15:12.679
Besides Your Majesty,

00:15:13.320 --> 00:15:14.720
I have Jiang Tang,

00:15:15.120 --> 00:15:15.840
Hanying,

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:17.200
Jinming around me.

00:15:18.679 --> 00:15:20.679
And Huna who is far away in Dada.

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:23.000
I don't regret that.

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:26.720
My only regret

00:15:30.039 --> 00:15:31.799
is the child in my womb

00:15:32.480 --> 00:15:34.320
who hasn't had the chance
to see this world

00:15:35.879 --> 00:15:37.600
and now must go with its mother.

00:15:37.679 --> 00:15:38.519
Xu Yu.

00:15:41.720 --> 00:15:43.039
Don't say that word.

00:15:44.600 --> 00:15:45.519
I command you.

00:15:46.919 --> 00:15:48.639
You must live well.

00:15:50.759 --> 00:15:51.759
Xiao Jinyun.

00:15:54.559 --> 00:15:55.519
In this lifetime,

00:15:56.679 --> 00:15:58.639
I've never regretted marrying you

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:01.960
because I couldn't love anyone else,

00:16:03.200 --> 00:16:04.480
not as a child,

00:16:06.519 --> 00:16:07.480
not ever.

00:16:15.000 --> 00:16:16.000
(Xiao Jinyun,)

00:16:17.039 --> 00:16:18.440
(meeting you,)

00:16:18.799 --> 00:16:19.799
(getting to know you)

00:16:20.200 --> 00:16:21.080
(and loving you)

00:16:21.919 --> 00:16:24.000
(is the luckiest thing
that has ever happened to me.)

00:16:25.120 --> 00:16:28.080
(Even though we've had
misunderstandings and disagreements,)

00:16:28.840 --> 00:16:30.360
(in my memory,)

00:16:30.799 --> 00:16:34.399
(the happy moments
we shared are the clearest.)

00:16:34.759 --> 00:16:38.440
(They have made my life complete)

00:16:38.759 --> 00:16:39.559
(and regretless.)

00:16:41.919 --> 00:16:43.120
So, Xiao Jinyun,

00:16:46.679 --> 00:16:48.759
if I'm no longer in this world someday,

00:16:49.840 --> 00:16:51.240
don't be too sad.

00:16:53.559 --> 00:16:55.759
We have so many memories.

00:16:57.320 --> 00:16:58.799
When you miss me,

00:17:00.039 --> 00:17:02.000
just recall those memories.

00:17:06.279 --> 00:17:07.720
But don't recall for too long.

00:17:09.799 --> 00:17:11.079
We live in this world.

00:17:12.119 --> 00:17:15.240
The future is always
much more important than the past.

00:17:16.279 --> 00:17:16.839
Right?

00:17:18.319 --> 00:17:19.319
I tell you.

00:17:21.480 --> 00:17:24.160
You can't just walk away.

00:17:43.198 --> 00:17:48.382
♪Parting clouds
to pluck the waxing moon♪

00:17:49.118 --> 00:17:53.681
♪Brewing a pot of bygone years♪

00:17:55.006 --> 00:18:00.421
♪Chill flame, window shade,
console my grieving soul♪

00:18:00.990 --> 00:18:05.534
♪Drunk through lifetimes
with no dreams returned♪

00:18:06.174 --> 00:18:11.438
♪If not for letting go, how could I
bear to shatter this dream♪

00:18:11.806 --> 00:18:17.483
♪Returning to drift
through the mortal world♪

00:18:17.822 --> 00:18:19.838
♪Like her, like me, like you♪

00:18:20.030 --> 00:18:23.774
♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

00:18:24.350 --> 00:18:29.022
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

00:18:29.566 --> 00:18:31.326
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

00:18:31.646 --> 00:18:35.262
♪Loving, hurting,
and regretting our late meeting♪

00:18:35.509 --> 00:18:41.036
♪Tell me, after all this entanglement,
who regrets it more♪